1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,980
Let Me Do It!!

2
00:00:00,820 --> 00:00:02,720
Let me do it!

3
00:00:04,980 --> 00:00:09,190
Toushin High School

4
00:00:05,710 --> 00:00:08,300
<i>On the way home from cram school...</i>

5
00:00:09,190 --> 00:00:11,610
Man, that was rough.

6
00:00:11,610 --> 00:00:14,280
Right? I'm exhausted.

7
00:00:14,280 --> 00:00:16,620
Oh, are you on your way home now?

8
00:00:17,330 --> 00:00:20,580
Such a coincidence. I was just 
going home from my walk.

9
00:00:20,580 --> 00:00:21,810
President!

10
00:00:21,810 --> 00:00:23,660
It's Takane-chan!

11
00:00:23,960 --> 00:00:26,360
If you're both so tired,

12
00:00:26,360 --> 00:00:28,630
why don't we go take a break somewhere?

13
00:00:28,630 --> 00:00:30,480
Oh, I have an idea!

14
00:00:30,480 --> 00:00:32,720
There's this family restaurant I often go to.

15
00:00:34,930 --> 00:00:37,390
Hiring
 part-time 
workers!!!!

16
00:00:34,930 --> 00:00:37,390
Now serving new desserts!

17
00:00:38,100 --> 00:00:40,600
<i>I wonder if President will be all right...</i>

18
00:00:40,600 --> 00:00:44,560
<i>She generally doesn't show 
strong emotions towards anyone,</i>

19
00:00:44,560 --> 00:00:46,940
<i>but the other day at the park...</i>

20
00:00:49,850 --> 00:00:51,400
Welcom—

21
00:00:52,010 --> 00:00:55,360
Ellie, you really don't get tired 
of this place, huh?

22
00:00:56,430 --> 00:00:58,840
I actually came from my cram school today.

23
00:00:58,840 --> 00:01:00,370
I see.

24
00:01:00,370 --> 00:01:01,950
And what would you like to order?

25
00:01:01,950 --> 00:01:05,660
We'll start with a mountain of fries 
and three cups for the drink bar.

26
00:01:05,660 --> 00:01:07,750
Coming right up.

27
00:01:08,090 --> 00:01:10,400
Oh, and my shift will be done in an hour.

28
00:01:10,400 --> 00:01:11,590
Roger that.

29
00:01:12,030 --> 00:01:14,170
You know that waitress?

30
00:01:14,170 --> 00:01:16,470
Yeah, she's from my high school.

31
00:01:16,740 --> 00:01:18,270
Don't tell anyone,

32
00:01:18,270 --> 00:01:20,770
but she makes the portion of fries extra big!

33
00:01:20,770 --> 00:01:23,310
So that's why you picked this place.

34
00:01:23,310 --> 00:01:25,390
It'll be my treat!

35
00:01:25,390 --> 00:01:26,670
So let's all eat together!

36
00:01:26,670 --> 00:01:28,730
Really? Thanks!

37
00:01:28,730 --> 00:01:32,020
I'm sorry, I try not to eat 
too many carbohydrates.

38
00:01:32,020 --> 00:01:34,610
Oh, I'm sorry, I didn't know!

39
00:01:34,610 --> 00:01:37,770
Makes sense, though! 
You have an amazing figure.

40
00:01:40,630 --> 00:01:43,120
So how's cram school?

41
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,480
Oh, right.

42
00:01:44,480 --> 00:01:47,970
They do review sessions and also offer 
guidance for my weaker subjects,

43
00:01:47,970 --> 00:01:49,840
so I'm able to keep up so far.

44
00:01:50,960 --> 00:01:52,090
I see.

45
00:01:53,170 --> 00:01:56,020
And it's a relief to have 
Ellie-chan in my class.

46
00:01:56,020 --> 00:01:58,360
That keeps me from getting too nervous.

47
00:01:58,360 --> 00:02:00,140
Oh, same for me!

48
00:02:01,220 --> 00:02:07,060
I mean, I never thought we'd be studying 
together again once we entered high school.

49
00:02:08,490 --> 00:02:12,230
We used to do homework together a lot
when we were in grade school.

50
00:02:13,290 --> 00:02:18,760
Oh, so you like studying 
with girls, huh, Shirota-kun?

51
00:02:20,230 --> 00:02:23,010
You insisted on coming over the other day

52
00:02:23,010 --> 00:02:25,620
because you wanted my help with school work, too.

53
00:02:25,620 --> 00:02:29,070
Despite the fact that my parents 
were away that night...

54
00:02:29,070 --> 00:02:30,280
Actually, that time was...

55
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:31,700
That makes sense!

56
00:02:31,700 --> 00:02:35,590
Figures that you're just as smart 
as you used to be, Takane-chan!

57
00:02:36,750 --> 00:02:40,060
If only you had been there back then...

58
00:02:37,300 --> 00:02:42,930
Big Strawberry

59
00:02:40,060 --> 00:02:44,890
The only memories I have are of us 
abandoning our homework and playing.

60
00:02:45,630 --> 00:02:47,100
I wonder.

61
00:02:47,460 --> 00:02:49,000
Even if I had been there,

62
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:52,310
I might not have been a match 
for Shirota-kun's fickle nature.

63
00:02:52,690 --> 00:02:54,200
The other time, too...

64
00:02:55,480 --> 00:02:57,420
He couldn't focus on studying anymore,

65
00:02:57,420 --> 00:03:02,060
so he strong-armed me into cosplaying
as a cat to clear his head.

66
00:03:02,060 --> 00:03:03,950
Wha?! No, that was your—

67
00:03:03,950 --> 00:03:05,860
That sounds so fun!

68
00:03:05,860 --> 00:03:07,160
Was it Halloween?

69
00:03:07,160 --> 00:03:08,210
<i>Halloween?!</i>

70
00:03:08,210 --> 00:03:11,660
Oh yeah, let's all hold a group 
study session together!

71
00:03:11,660 --> 00:03:14,570
And maybe a sleepover afterwards.

72
00:03:14,570 --> 00:03:17,600
Just the group study session, maybe.

73
00:03:17,600 --> 00:03:19,570
Oh, come on.

74
00:03:19,570 --> 00:03:22,760
We used to do sleepovers 
all the time before!

75
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:23,800
Ellie-san.

76
00:03:24,690 --> 00:03:27,800
That is an extremely dangerous suggestion.

77
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:28,770
Because...

78
00:03:29,770 --> 00:03:35,000
Not only did he stay the night saying 
the heavy rain prevented him from going home,

79
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:38,230
but he also pushed 
my unclad body to the ground.

80
00:03:38,230 --> 00:03:40,690
T-That was you! The lightni—

81
00:03:40,690 --> 00:03:42,660
What's that about lightning?

82
00:03:43,660 --> 00:03:45,470
Unclad? What does that mean?

83
00:03:45,470 --> 00:03:47,740
<i>Phew, she didn't get it.</i>

84
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:52,450
Um, President, is everything all right?

85
00:03:52,450 --> 00:03:54,380
It seems you're on edge or something...

86
00:03:54,870 --> 00:03:57,090
I think it's quite natural 
for me to be on alert.

87
00:03:57,690 --> 00:04:01,010
She only knows 
the pure you from the past.

88
00:04:01,010 --> 00:04:06,300
I am revealing to her that you've become 
a degenerate controlled by your desires.

89
00:04:06,590 --> 00:04:09,390
Hold on, like half of that was made up!

90
00:04:10,220 --> 00:04:12,140
Oh, is it, though?

91
00:04:12,440 --> 00:04:15,020
It seems we have a discrepancy 
in what we remember.

92
00:04:15,020 --> 00:04:18,610
Even then, it can't hurt to listen to my side.

93
00:04:18,610 --> 00:04:24,310
After all, I'm the one who understands 
the current you better than her.

94
00:04:25,200 --> 00:04:26,960
Still...

95
00:04:30,620 --> 00:04:32,570
All right, see you...

96
00:04:32,570 --> 00:04:33,960
Ellie-san.

97
00:04:33,960 --> 00:04:37,400
Please be sufficiently wary 
of Shirota-kun's behavior.

98
00:04:37,400 --> 00:04:38,840
You're still on that?!

99
00:04:39,200 --> 00:04:40,850
Oh, Takane-chan!

100
00:04:40,850 --> 00:04:42,800
Could we maybe talk?

101
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:44,690
I don't mind...

102
00:04:44,690 --> 00:04:47,490
Kou-chan, I'll see you tomorrow at cram school!

103
00:04:47,490 --> 00:04:49,040
Yeah, sure.

104
00:04:50,510 --> 00:04:52,210
<i>I wonder what's going on.</i>

105
00:04:52,210 --> 00:04:55,860
<i>Can I really leave those two alone?</i>

106
00:04:57,410 --> 00:04:59,880
What did you want to talk about?

107
00:04:59,880 --> 00:05:01,440
I'm sorry, Takane-chan.

108
00:05:01,440 --> 00:05:03,080
I didn't realize.

109
00:05:03,080 --> 00:05:04,400
What do you mean?

110
00:05:04,400 --> 00:05:06,830
You came to our cram school 
because you're worried

111
00:05:06,830 --> 00:05:11,460
that I like Kou-chan and that I'm 
making moves on him, right?

112
00:05:11,460 --> 00:05:12,910
W-What are you talking abou—

113
00:05:12,910 --> 00:05:15,520
And then I did it again...

114
00:05:15,520 --> 00:05:19,000
Having fun recounting the good times 
I had with Kou-chan in the past...

115
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:20,590
I'm really sorry!

116
00:05:20,590 --> 00:05:22,330
I made you feel jealous.

117
00:05:22,330 --> 00:05:23,960
H-Hold on!

118
00:05:23,960 --> 00:05:25,860
You're stacking theory on delusion and—

119
00:05:25,860 --> 00:05:27,090
But don't worry!

120
00:05:27,340 --> 00:05:30,730
Kou-chan and I are 
totally not like that at all.

121
00:05:30,730 --> 00:05:32,560
I mean, I'm with someone!

122
00:05:33,190 --> 00:05:35,130
Oh... really?

123
00:05:35,130 --> 00:05:35,860
Yes.

124
00:05:36,270 --> 00:05:40,480
If anything, I'd be more 
into you than Kou-chan...

125
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,820
Just kidding.

126
00:05:41,820 --> 00:05:42,480
Wha?

127
00:05:44,850 --> 00:05:46,520
Ellie, sorry for the wait.

128
00:05:46,520 --> 00:05:48,610
Oh, no worries.

129
00:05:48,610 --> 00:05:50,260
Well, I'm going home then.

130
00:05:50,260 --> 00:05:52,820
You take care on the way home, Takane-chan!

131
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:55,130
S-Sure...

132
00:06:08,990 --> 00:06:10,640
What's this?

133
00:06:10,640 --> 00:06:12,060
Were you waiting for me?

134
00:06:12,060 --> 00:06:14,850
You look like the bronze statue 
in front of Shibuya Station.

135
00:06:14,850 --> 00:06:16,950
Did you just compare me to Hachikou?!

136
00:06:17,330 --> 00:06:20,060
So what did you talk about?

137
00:06:20,400 --> 00:06:24,320
We had a lecture about 
how you're lust incarnate.

138
00:06:24,320 --> 00:06:25,780
You're joking, right?!

139
00:06:26,230 --> 00:06:27,480
I'm joking.

140
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:29,900
We only talked about trivial matters.

141
00:06:29,900 --> 00:06:32,170
I see...

142
00:06:32,730 --> 00:06:35,490
Well, if I had to say one thing,

143
00:06:35,490 --> 00:06:40,460
it's that I realized I've been 
unjustly suspicious of her.

144
00:06:42,840 --> 00:06:46,340
Ellie, that girl is your type, isn't she?

145
00:06:46,340 --> 00:06:48,080
You realized?!

146
00:06:48,080 --> 00:06:51,390
It's fine, though! We're just friends!

147
00:06:52,540 --> 00:06:53,970
This reminds me...

148
00:06:54,460 --> 00:06:59,000
The other day, Ellie-san foisted 
these leftover ones onto me.

149
00:06:57,810 --> 00:07:00,940
Water Balloons

150
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,940
Oh, really?

151
00:07:01,380 --> 00:07:03,110
How about we have some fun?

152
00:07:03,110 --> 00:07:03,940
Huh?

153
00:07:06,050 --> 00:07:09,330
The one who lands more hits 
with the balloons wins.

154
00:07:09,330 --> 00:07:12,110
The victor gets to make 
one demand of the loser.

155
00:07:12,450 --> 00:07:14,060
What do you say?

156
00:07:14,060 --> 00:07:15,870
You really want to do this?

157
00:07:16,150 --> 00:07:16,980
What now?

158
00:07:16,980 --> 00:07:20,280
You're saying you can do it 
with Ellie-san, but not with me?

159
00:07:20,280 --> 00:07:23,080
N-No! That's not what I meant...

160
00:07:25,670 --> 00:07:27,630
After some back and forth, it begins

161
00:07:28,280 --> 00:07:32,470
<i>I doubt I stand a chance against her, 
even if I play to win.</i>

162
00:07:33,110 --> 00:07:37,430
<i>Even then, I can't risk dousing her in water,</i>

163
00:07:37,940 --> 00:07:39,890
<i>so I need to be careful not to hit her!</i>

164
00:07:45,210 --> 00:07:46,990
Not bad, Shirota-kun.

165
00:07:46,990 --> 00:07:48,860
You got the first hit on me.

166
00:07:48,860 --> 00:07:51,020
Um, I don't think that one was really...

167
00:07:51,020 --> 00:07:52,580
Oh, no.

168
00:07:52,580 --> 00:07:53,530
What's wrong?

169
00:07:55,220 --> 00:07:57,400
My bra is visible now...

170
00:07:57,400 --> 00:07:58,720
Quite skillful.

171
00:07:58,720 --> 00:08:00,030
Was that on purpose?

172
00:08:00,030 --> 00:08:01,250
Wha?! I'm sorry!

173
00:08:01,250 --> 00:08:02,670
<i>Wait...</i>

174
00:08:02,670 --> 00:08:04,890
<i>This situation seems familiar.</i>

175
00:08:05,750 --> 00:08:08,670
<i>Oh yeah, it's like when Ellie and I played.</i>

176
00:08:09,130 --> 00:08:13,630
<i>But that time, it wasn't that 
her bra became visible.</i>

177
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:21,000
Say. Care to explain why 
you seem so distracted?

178
00:08:21,870 --> 00:08:26,690
Don't tell me you and she experienced 
something more than her bra becoming visible?

179
00:08:26,690 --> 00:08:32,440
<i>Wait, was she watching Ellie 
and me from the beginning that day?!</i>

180
00:08:32,860 --> 00:08:34,430
N-N-Not really?!

181
00:08:34,430 --> 00:08:36,670
That's not...

182
00:08:40,920 --> 00:08:44,880
I meant to toy with you more 
by feigning a close fight,

183
00:08:44,880 --> 00:08:47,000
but I accidentally ended you in an instant.

184
00:08:50,210 --> 00:08:54,170
Now, what will I order the loser to do...?

185
00:08:54,490 --> 00:08:56,710
Please go easy on me.

186
00:08:57,350 --> 00:08:58,510
Let me think...

187
00:09:00,150 --> 00:09:02,220
Right, then how about this.

188
00:09:03,030 --> 00:09:06,780
I worked up a sweat, 
so I'll have you lick it up.

189
00:09:06,780 --> 00:09:08,060
S-Say what?!

190
00:09:08,450 --> 00:09:09,920
What is that even?!

191
00:09:11,500 --> 00:09:14,150
<i>This also kind of reminds me 
of that other situation...</i>

192
00:09:15,240 --> 00:09:19,160
<i>Could it be that she's deliberately 
recreating the events of that day?</i>

193
00:09:20,540 --> 00:09:22,210
Um, President,

194
00:09:22,210 --> 00:09:27,390
are you still mad about me taking my plans 
for the future lightly and playing around?

195
00:09:27,390 --> 00:09:29,540
Is there any reason for me to be mad?

196
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:34,510
Right now, you're earnestly engaging 
with shaping your own future.

197
00:09:35,140 --> 00:09:38,830
Then it doesn't have to be 
such an abnormal order.

198
00:09:38,830 --> 00:09:40,800
We're in a public park, too.

199
00:09:40,800 --> 00:09:44,730
Besides, me licking it would make it dirty.

200
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:46,730
It's fine.

201
00:09:46,730 --> 00:09:49,420
We're the only ones here.

202
00:09:49,420 --> 00:09:51,940
And it wouldn't be dirty.

203
00:09:53,940 --> 00:09:55,730
I'll disinfect it when I get home.

204
00:09:55,730 --> 00:09:58,360
Then wouldn't it be better 
if I didn't do it at all?!

205
00:09:58,700 --> 00:09:59,630
So what?

206
00:09:59,630 --> 00:10:02,730
Having your neck licked by a girl is fine,

207
00:10:02,730 --> 00:10:04,690
but you can't do the licking yourself?

208
00:10:04,690 --> 00:10:06,460
<i>So she </i>is<i> holding a grudge?!</i>

209
00:10:06,810 --> 00:10:09,080
That's not really it.

210
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:11,520
Then hurry up and follow the order.

211
00:10:13,670 --> 00:10:16,380
So... the sweat on your neck?

212
00:10:16,380 --> 00:10:17,580
What?

213
00:10:17,580 --> 00:10:19,590
Who said anything about my neck?

214
00:10:20,070 --> 00:10:21,760
Take a good look.

215
00:10:21,760 --> 00:10:24,060
There's no sweat anywhere on my neck.

216
00:10:25,750 --> 00:10:27,600
But under my clothes...

217
00:10:29,030 --> 00:10:30,900
my armpits...

218
00:10:30,900 --> 00:10:32,160
my chest...

219
00:10:33,550 --> 00:10:36,820
my stomach, and my inner thighs.

220
00:10:38,660 --> 00:10:41,300
If you were to lick, 
those would probably be the areas.

221
00:10:41,300 --> 00:10:43,930
I'll be generous and allow you to pick a spot.

222
00:10:43,930 --> 00:10:45,760
All of those are impossible!

223
00:10:47,050 --> 00:10:50,340
Sheesh, I know in reality 
you want to lick all of it.

224
00:10:50,340 --> 00:10:52,380
Still pretending not to be a perv.

225
00:10:52,380 --> 00:10:57,340
You know I could force you 
to do my entire body, right?

226
00:10:57,340 --> 00:11:00,760
<i>I-Is she really planning on making me do this?</i>

227
00:11:01,270 --> 00:11:04,520
<i>Once she makes up her mind, 
there's no force that can change it.</i>

228
00:11:04,520 --> 00:11:06,850
<i>That means I have to pick 
a relatively safe spot</i>

229
00:11:07,590 --> 00:11:10,660
<i>before she gets even more outrageous ideas!</i>

230
00:11:12,930 --> 00:11:15,230
Well, please go ahead.

231
00:11:15,230 --> 00:11:16,730
O-Okay...

232
00:11:17,700 --> 00:11:22,030
<i>I thought that the stomach was the most 
normal place given the choices...</i>

233
00:11:26,890 --> 00:11:29,870
<i>But when I think about it, 
it's not normal at all!</i>

234
00:11:29,870 --> 00:11:32,420
<i>With Ellie-chan, I was on the receiving end...</i>

235
00:11:32,420 --> 00:11:37,250
<i>but this time, I have to actively do 
it to President's stomach...</i>

236
00:11:37,550 --> 00:11:39,620
When you stare that intently,

237
00:11:39,620 --> 00:11:42,590
it almost makes me sweat more.

238
00:11:42,590 --> 00:11:44,680
I'm sorry!

239
00:11:45,350 --> 00:11:48,990
<i>Her skin... it's almost translucent...</i>

240
00:11:48,990 --> 00:11:50,790
<i>it smells so good...</i>

241
00:11:50,790 --> 00:11:53,360
<i>and now the moisture 
trailing down this skin is...</i>

242
00:11:54,770 --> 00:11:57,210
Come on, hurry.

243
00:12:11,490 --> 00:12:13,850
Good work, Licky-ta-kun.

244
00:12:13,850 --> 00:12:15,960
You weren't half bad.

245
00:12:16,370 --> 00:12:20,050
Oh, and just so you know,

246
00:12:20,050 --> 00:12:23,930
you best not waste time deeply 
pondering, "What was this for?".

247
00:12:24,310 --> 00:12:27,370
I haven't been paying 
too much attention to you lately,

248
00:12:27,370 --> 00:12:29,370
so that's why I spent time with you.

249
00:12:29,370 --> 00:12:31,430
That's the only reason.

250
00:12:33,540 --> 00:12:37,710
With that said, if today's 
experience was too intense

251
00:12:39,010 --> 00:12:44,350
and ends up overwriting your memories 
of being in this park with her, I'm sorry.

252
00:12:45,780 --> 00:12:51,580
<i>At that time, I felt like I heard something 
that sounded like her core motivation...</i>

253
00:12:52,770 --> 00:12:54,070
Shirota-kun?

254
00:12:56,290 --> 00:12:57,630
Shirota-kun?!

255
00:12:58,110 --> 00:13:00,410
<i>But the fever got to that memory,</i>

256
00:13:00,410 --> 00:13:03,150
<i>and it faded along with my swirling vision.</i>

257
00:13:03,470 --> 00:13:05,200
Hold on!

258
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:07,370
I'll undo it right away!

259
00:13:07,970 --> 00:13:12,970
<i></i><i>Please</i>

260
00:13:07,970 --> 00:13:12,970
<i></i><i>Put Them On, 
Takamine-san</i>

261
00:13:12,970 --> 00:13:17,980
<i></i><i>Please</i>

262
00:13:12,970 --> 00:13:17,980
<i></i><i>Put Them On, 
Takamine-san</i>

263
00:13:19,030 --> 00:13:21,190
<i>It's the last day of summer break.</i>

264
00:13:21,530 --> 00:13:24,830
<i>We've come to a leisure 
facility in our prefecture.</i>

265
00:13:26,220 --> 00:13:28,360
That's quite a nice view.

266
00:13:28,360 --> 00:13:32,020
It's my first time here too, 
but it's really nice.

267
00:13:32,490 --> 00:13:34,960
<i></i>Toushin 
High School

268
00:13:33,330 --> 00:13:34,960
<i>Earlier that week...</i>

269
00:13:35,260 --> 00:13:38,670
<i>After finishing the summer classes 
at cram school,</i>

270
00:13:39,060 --> 00:13:41,380
<i>I received a message from the president.</i>

271
00:13:42,940 --> 00:13:45,900
This seems ideal for unwinding.

272
00:13:45,900 --> 00:13:47,600
Let's go.

273
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:48,340
Okay.

274
00:13:49,380 --> 00:13:54,380
<i>President said she'd help me study 
after the summer classes were over,</i>

275
00:13:55,110 --> 00:13:57,740
<i>and that she doesn't really
want anything in return.</i>

276
00:13:58,430 --> 00:14:01,850
<i>But I still want to repay her somehow!</i>

277
00:14:01,850 --> 00:14:03,660
<i>I've studied up on this place, too,</i>

278
00:14:03,660 --> 00:14:07,110
<i>so I'm going to be a good host 
and have her enjoy herself!</i>

279
00:14:07,550 --> 00:14:09,280
Where do you want to go first?

280
00:14:09,280 --> 00:14:11,700
If you have any preferences, 
I don't mind hearing them.

281
00:14:11,700 --> 00:14:15,540
Oh, then why don't we get some 
drinks before we set out?

282
00:14:15,540 --> 00:14:18,860
There's a cafe that offers 
takeout right there.

283
00:14:18,860 --> 00:14:20,500
Let's do that.

284
00:14:20,900 --> 00:14:24,420
Oh, that reminds me of a coincidence.

285
00:14:24,900 --> 00:14:29,940
I received two drink coupons 
from an acquaintance.

286
00:14:29,940 --> 00:14:31,340
Be grateful.

287
00:14:31,340 --> 00:14:33,060
I'll treat you to a cu—

288
00:14:36,490 --> 00:14:37,850
I got them!

289
00:14:37,850 --> 00:14:39,640
Black is fine, right?

290
00:14:39,640 --> 00:14:40,690
What about the money?

291
00:14:40,690 --> 00:14:43,210
Oh, it's my treat.

292
00:14:43,210 --> 00:14:45,400
I mean, you invited me out today!

293
00:14:55,620 --> 00:14:58,200
I was feeling like a vanilla latte today.

294
00:14:58,200 --> 00:14:59,570
As a closet,

295
00:14:59,570 --> 00:15:02,750
you're supposed to sense what your 
owner wants the most and bring that.

296
00:15:03,610 --> 00:15:06,710
Here, you may have these coupons.

297
00:15:06,710 --> 00:15:08,210
R-Right.

298
00:15:15,710 --> 00:15:17,920
What are you standing around for?

299
00:15:17,920 --> 00:15:19,510
Hurry and put them on me.

300
00:15:20,530 --> 00:15:22,100
Oh, right!

301
00:15:22,520 --> 00:15:25,570
<i>She went behind the building by herself?</i>

302
00:15:26,130 --> 00:15:28,800
<i>That basically never happens...</i>

303
00:15:30,290 --> 00:15:32,490
What should we do next?

304
00:15:32,840 --> 00:15:36,060
Apparently there's a Nordic 
general goods store up ahead.

305
00:15:36,060 --> 00:15:37,550
Could we go there?

306
00:15:37,550 --> 00:15:39,300
Sure, that's fine.

307
00:15:46,930 --> 00:15:48,340
Looks like this is it.

308
00:16:01,250 --> 00:16:03,560
That's pretty cute.

309
00:16:03,560 --> 00:16:05,100
It's got a warmth to it.

310
00:16:05,100 --> 00:16:06,400
You think so?

311
00:16:07,180 --> 00:16:08,260
<i>Yes!</i>

312
00:16:09,310 --> 00:16:11,530
Excuse me, I'm going to the bathroom.

313
00:16:11,530 --> 00:16:12,330
Sure.

314
00:16:15,350 --> 00:16:18,240
Was there anything that caught your eye?

315
00:16:18,240 --> 00:16:21,790
I thought the carved wood coasters looked nice.

316
00:16:21,790 --> 00:16:25,090
And you were intrigued by that 
stuffed animal, right?

317
00:16:25,090 --> 00:16:26,530
Not really.

318
00:16:26,530 --> 00:16:27,180
Oh...

319
00:16:27,640 --> 00:16:30,960
I did say it was cute, but I don't need it.

320
00:16:31,780 --> 00:16:38,050
Gazing at a mirror is much more soothing for 
my soul than staring at a stuffed animal.

321
00:16:38,050 --> 00:16:40,140
Oh, I'm sorry.

322
00:16:40,140 --> 00:16:46,860
I actually got you this as a present 
for inviting me today...

323
00:16:48,510 --> 00:16:50,560
Um, President?

324
00:16:58,470 --> 00:17:03,520
I'd rather turn it around and gift you 
something before accepting any alms from you.

325
00:17:03,520 --> 00:17:05,390
Carved wood coaster, right?

326
00:17:05,390 --> 00:17:06,520
<i>But why?!</i>

327
00:17:07,460 --> 00:17:10,190
<i>I only had good intentions...</i>

328
00:17:11,580 --> 00:17:14,040
So, what are we doing next?

329
00:17:14,040 --> 00:17:15,970
Oh, then right here.

330
00:17:16,490 --> 00:17:19,310
It seems you can get on a boat.

331
00:17:19,310 --> 00:17:21,180
I've never been on one,

332
00:17:21,490 --> 00:17:23,120
but what do you think?

333
00:17:23,120 --> 00:17:25,820
Well, if you want to try it.

334
00:17:27,660 --> 00:17:29,730
This feels nice.

335
00:17:29,730 --> 00:17:32,400
I don't know if it's because we're floating.

336
00:17:32,400 --> 00:17:33,520
You're right.

337
00:17:33,860 --> 00:17:37,700
Being on a boat feels nicer than I expected.

338
00:17:37,700 --> 00:17:38,830
Oh?

339
00:17:38,830 --> 00:17:41,200
So it's your first time on a boat, too?

340
00:17:41,610 --> 00:17:43,470
You've got so many experiences,

341
00:17:43,470 --> 00:17:45,660
I thought you'd done this already as well.

342
00:17:45,660 --> 00:17:50,680
E-Even I can have first times...

343
00:17:50,680 --> 00:17:51,710
I-Is that wrong?

344
00:17:51,710 --> 00:17:53,530
N-No.

345
00:17:54,360 --> 00:17:57,400
Anyway, I'll take over rowing for you.

346
00:17:57,400 --> 00:18:00,260
Seeing you totally exhausted 
isn't pleasant.

347
00:18:02,020 --> 00:18:04,010
No, I'm still fine!

348
00:18:04,010 --> 00:18:07,440
Hey, I said I'd take over!

349
00:18:07,440 --> 00:18:10,020
I'm really fine!

350
00:18:13,820 --> 00:18:14,520
Jump!

351
00:18:14,520 --> 00:18:16,270
What?!

352
00:18:17,090 --> 00:18:18,570
P-President?!

353
00:18:25,910 --> 00:18:28,410
Oh no.

354
00:18:28,410 --> 00:18:31,250
I accidentally slipped.

355
00:18:31,250 --> 00:18:33,900
Yeah, no, that was on purpose.

356
00:18:33,900 --> 00:18:37,470
I don't like using my ability 
for things like this,

357
00:18:37,470 --> 00:18:40,580
but I also can't stay in these wet clothes...

358
00:18:48,830 --> 00:18:51,550
<i>She undid it to the point 
before we got on the boat?</i>

359
00:18:51,980 --> 00:18:54,130
<i>But where is she?</i>

360
00:18:54,130 --> 00:18:55,370
Sheesh.

361
00:18:57,880 --> 00:19:00,590
Um, President... what are you...

362
00:19:00,590 --> 00:19:02,180
Don't "what are you" me.

363
00:19:02,180 --> 00:19:04,330
Stop looking so confused already.

364
00:19:04,640 --> 00:19:07,580
So, where do you want to go next?

365
00:19:07,580 --> 00:19:11,040
If you dawdle too long, 
the day is going to end.

366
00:19:11,370 --> 00:19:13,610
That's not what I meant.

367
00:19:14,250 --> 00:19:16,720
Why did you put them on yourself?

368
00:19:20,430 --> 00:19:24,500
Th-This is because you were 
so dense, I couldn't wait anymore.

369
00:19:24,500 --> 00:19:27,150
You better repent for causing me this trouble!

370
00:19:27,150 --> 00:19:28,790
I'm sorry!

371
00:19:30,020 --> 00:19:33,040
<i>I was supposed to be a good host for her today.</i>

372
00:19:33,040 --> 00:19:35,510
<i>I'm just making her more and more displeased.</i>

373
00:19:35,860 --> 00:19:38,520
<i>I wonder what I did wrong.</i>

374
00:19:42,830 --> 00:19:44,110
I'm sorry.

375
00:19:44,110 --> 00:19:46,620
It seems whatever I'm doing is unnecessary.

376
00:19:47,250 --> 00:19:49,780
No, that's not it.

377
00:19:50,520 --> 00:19:54,380
I don't know why, 
but you're putting up a big front today.

378
00:19:54,710 --> 00:19:59,460
At this rate, the only thing you'll 
gain from today is the exhaustion.

379
00:20:01,480 --> 00:20:05,260
I've been trying
to show you my appreciation.

380
00:20:07,040 --> 00:20:08,240
As a reward...

381
00:20:08,240 --> 00:20:12,270
for working hard on summer classes...

382
00:20:12,810 --> 00:20:14,040
Wha?

383
00:20:14,040 --> 00:20:15,390
<i>Could it be...</i>

384
00:20:16,170 --> 00:20:18,830
<i>That the reason 
she was being weird all day is...</i>

385
00:20:19,480 --> 00:20:22,460
<i>that she was looking out for me?</i>

386
00:20:24,430 --> 00:20:25,280
What?

387
00:20:25,280 --> 00:20:28,410
Why do you look so utterly shocked?

388
00:20:28,990 --> 00:20:33,410
I-I specifically wanted to reward you.

389
00:20:33,410 --> 00:20:37,620
If anything, not accepting that 
with gratitude is wrong.

390
00:20:39,500 --> 00:20:41,300
Thank you so much!

391
00:20:41,300 --> 00:20:43,060
But I'm fine!

392
00:20:45,070 --> 00:20:48,600
You're already treating me well enough.

393
00:20:49,250 --> 00:20:52,170
Not only are you helping me 
study for the entrance exams,

394
00:20:52,560 --> 00:20:56,380
but more importantly, I'm more 
optimistic now thanks to you.

395
00:20:57,960 --> 00:20:59,270
Besides...

396
00:21:00,290 --> 00:21:04,810
Last night, I put together a plan for today,
 trying to come up with things

397
00:21:04,810 --> 00:21:06,890
that you would enjoy.

398
00:21:07,650 --> 00:21:11,000
That's already enough for me to have fun.

399
00:21:15,650 --> 00:21:19,160
Huh, look at you with your smug lines.

400
00:21:19,160 --> 00:21:20,800
W-Was that smug?

401
00:21:21,220 --> 00:21:25,380
Besides, if you think someone 
like you could bring me joy,

402
00:21:25,740 --> 00:21:28,900
I must have sunken quite low in your eyes.

403
00:21:28,900 --> 00:21:31,280
W-Wha?! No, that's not what I...

404
00:21:36,850 --> 00:21:38,240
You're really...

405
00:21:42,470 --> 00:21:43,880
so cocky.

406
00:21:49,930 --> 00:21:50,960
Well, then.

407
00:21:50,960 --> 00:21:54,690
Why don't I take you up on your offer 
and hear what you've planned next.

408
00:21:54,690 --> 00:21:55,460
Huh?

409
00:21:55,910 --> 00:21:58,640
You were going to make sure 
I enjoyed myself, right?

410
00:22:01,580 --> 00:22:04,260
When you put me on the spot like that, 
I'm not so sure anymore...

